{"tid":451821,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"對眼無啦啦腫左","createTime":"2017-10-29T14:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T16:08:44.000Z","uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"38f06c5162fa9d9a56b13ba9f385585a92ae28c1","tid":451821,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:59:55.000Z","msg":"打打下機覺得對眼好攰，唔想睜開，就keep住&ldquo;無神咁睜眼&rdquo;<br />\n然後上下眼簾都好痕，好似被蚊叮咁一粒粒，逐d逐d咁腫，然後腫到成個眼簾都漲晒，漲到睜唔大對眼，變左小剛咁，已經滴左眼藥水<br />\n呢5年內都試過兩次係咁，前兩次係訓訓下晏覺，醒左feel到對眼好攰，唔想睜開，然後就開始腫痕<br />\n對眼keep住有眼水，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e063093e5ce1250107df78e3d2228d416b8ed01b","tid":451821,"uid":29441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T15:01:49.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦仲問"},{"pid":"afa530c3310b790d62a27e42899e839fa2c1f5d1","tid":451821,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T15:07:51.000Z","msg":"眼敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51032f5bdbce6bc17451b8e76ea764341a7b80a","tid":451821,"uid":20407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://tbdblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0535.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftbdblog.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2FIMG_0535.jpg&h=e4256f34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冷敷"},{"pid":"f722f55d21bedc03d05d07c75a060511fd248228","tid":451821,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"81b882ad562b15aed6571f1781a186438d72d154","tid":451821,"uid":4880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"去睇醫生"}]}